" />&lt;p>Ever come across the term &amp;ldquo;callback function&amp;rdquo; in web development and wondered what it actually means?&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Callback functions are fundamental to JavaScript and incredibly powerful. They&amp;rsquo;re the backbone of asynchronous operations and are used throughout modern web development. In this guide, I&amp;rsquo;ll break down what callback functions are and how to use them in straightforward terms.&lt;/p>
